      "messageBody": "Merge the latest Harness v1 core into the MastraCode runtime PR branch. Preserve the runtime adapter while forwarding explicit pending IDs through approval, question, plan, sandbox, and tool-suspension responses, and keep forked subagents under child permission gates instead of forcing yolo mode.",
      "messageHeadline": "fix(mastracode): refresh harness v1 runtime branch",
      "oid": "8567eba37eb17333b53f46a3bc22ac0467d12cbd"
    },
    {
      "authoredDate": "2026-05-24T20:11:01Z",
      "authors": [
        {
          "email": "mbenhamd@gmail.com",
          "id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2NzIwNDY3",
          "login": "mbenhamd",
          "name": "Mohamed BEN HAMDOUNE"
        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-05-24T20:11:01Z",
      "messageBody": "Add priority, deadline, and notBefore controls for Harness queue admissions.\n\nPersist and hash the scheduling inputs, enforce notBefore in the scheduler, and wake delayed queue items when they become runnable.\n\nThread the queue body fields through the server schema, generated client route types, and CLI route metadata.",
      "messageHeadline": "feat(core): add harness queue scheduling options",
      "oid": "318abc78300e901c596994fdfdf71ad7a5cc643d"
    },
    {
      "authoredDate": "2026-05-24T21:01:42Z",
      "authors": [
        {
          "email": "mbenhamd@gmail.com",
          "id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2NzIwNDY3",
          "login": "mbenhamd",
          "name": "Mohamed BEN HAMDOUNE"
        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-05-24T21:01:42Z",
      "messageBody": "Add reject/drop-oldest queue backpressure handling for Harness sessions.\n\nEmit queue_full_dropped evidence, fail dropped receipts, and settle dropped queue promises.\n\nReplace silent goal-continuation queue-full drops with durable events while preserving active and accepted recovery heads.",
      "messageHeadline": "feat(core): add harness queue backpressure",
      "oid": "704a3850214ab5fe3393064b9968c3a620f91816"
    },
    {
      "authoredDate": "2026-05-26T13:00:24Z",
